{"tid":293054,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打有整負離子","createTime":"2017-06-22T00:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T00:37:05.000Z","uid":121626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a82934f4d67b644ad01bff18d94a6bc56b2e4e1a","tid":293054,"uid":121626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T00:29:14.000Z","msg":"我最近整左負離子同剪短左 大概去到下巴咁長<br />\n整完都有兩日冇洗頭<br />\n但有時訓醒後面啲頭髮同側邊有啲會翹/彎左<br />\n要自己再夾 係唔係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係我整衰左？"},{"pid":"795fd4e9b3db773fad3beb0fb3d9bf9d59ba36c4","tid":293054,"uid":32831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T00:32:31.000Z","msg":"只要係肩以上又唔係男仔頭髮咁短 起身都好易變八爪魚"},{"pid":"4523cb79a7ba0cddcaf43906aeca1feec18c57b6","tid":293054,"uid":1998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T00:33:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只要係肩以上又唔係男仔頭髮咁短 起身都好易變八爪魚</blockquote><br />\n夠厚就唔會嘅<br />\n我頭髮薄就勁易成個章魚咁<br />\n樓豬仲要負離子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朝朝都早起攞哂啲時間去夾好佢"},{"pid":"0da5307ba9a7f072dd7a6349514466bb9adbcd04","tid":293054,"uid":32831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T00:34:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>只要係肩以上又唔係男仔頭髮咁短 起身都好易變八爪魚</blockquote><br />\n夠厚就唔會嘅<br />\n我頭髮薄就勁易成個章魚咁<br />\n樓豬仲要負離子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朝朝都早起攞哂啲時間去夾好佢</blockquote><br />\n所以有時候長頭髮仲無咁麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0382eddb00829fb67f10e95285606c20a2d061e9","tid":293054,"uid":121626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T00:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>只要係肩以上又唔係男仔頭髮咁短 起身都好易變八爪魚</blockquote><br />\n夠厚就唔會嘅<br />\n我頭髮薄就勁易成個章魚咁<br />\n樓豬仲要負離子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朝朝都早起攞哂啲時間去夾好佢</blockquote><br />\n所以有時候長頭髮仲無咁麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前我剪過次肩上都冇翹個啲<br />\n所以以為係負離子衰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來係因為太薄"}]}